This paper deals with the analysis of user reviews, which is a common topic in the field of computational linguistics (cs.CL). It also involves user behavior and decision-making, which falls under the category of human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The study uses an online experiment, which could be classified as a study in cybernetics (cs.CY). The paper also involves natural language processing techniques, which could be categorized under information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG).
